{"isSidechain":true,"agentId":"2d5be40f-7ed8-4fd","type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":"Plan critic RLM P09-1 (visual foundation), repo /usr/projects/Диплом, depth=complex. Round 2. Prior feedback incorporated:\n\n- Source assets: copied FROM /home/guihal/Стол/Правки/Изображения/ (logo.png, magic-spark.svg, magic-curl.svg, magic-orbit.svg, magic-thread.svg, magic-wisp.svg, tiny-spark.svg) INTO apps/mobile/app/assets/brand/. Verified these source files exist (ls confirmed). SVGs already aria-hidden + currentColor.\n- apps/mobile/visual.ts = `export * from \"../../shared/visual\"` (mirror api.ts).\n- tokens.scss keeps `--accent-weak` legacy token (used by P10 login.vue/FormField.vue/tailwind).\n- Logo.vue: import logo PNG in <script setup> via `import logoUrl from '~/assets/brand/chubzik-logo.png'`; use `mask: url(v-bind(logoUrl))` in <style>. Resolves via Nuxt/Vite.\n- raw-hex acceptance gate scoped to NEW + allowed paths only; pre-existing committed raw hex in tailwind.config.ts/AppButton.vue is out of write-scope (P10) and left untouched (not regressed, not introduced by this packet).\n\nPROJECT_RULES (unchanged excerpt): Files ≤150 LOC; backend source of truth; NO Math.random for visual; no Google Fonts CDN; raw hex only in tokens.scss + fallback theme file; VisualState fields fixed (no OD1 lilac / OD2 seed); Vue v-bind() in styles OK.\n\nALLOWED WRITE PATHS: shared/visual/**, apps/mobile/app/assets/**, apps/mobile/app/components/Logo.vue, apps/mobile/app/components/VisualBackground.vue, apps/mobile/app/assets/css/tokens.scss, MAY touch apps/mobile/nuxt.config.ts / apps/mobile/app/app.vue / apps/mobile/app/assets/css/main.scss.\n\nREVISED PLAN:\n\nFiles to create:\n1. apps/mobile/app/assets/css/tokens.scss (~115 LOC) — ALL raw hex ONLY here.\n   - Canonical color tokens (--bg #0D0F17, --surface #181B25, --surface-2 #222635, --stroke #30364A, --text #F4F0E8, --muted #9EA7B8, --magic #B9A7FF, --mana #8FD7C7, --xp #F6C76B, --blue #7EA7FF, --danger #FF6B7A), --accent default #7dd3fc (runtime, from catalog, non-lilac).\n   - Semantic aliases via var(): --brand-decoration-primary/secondary/muted, --magic-glow, --xp-accent, --background-orb-1/2, --decorative-opacity-low/medium.\n   - Legacy P10-compat utility tokens via var(): --accent-grad, --accent-2, --accent-weak (#2a2347 raw — was already raw in old main.scss, keep here), --glow-accent, --ring, --shadow-card, --error->danger, --ok->mana.\n   - Variant tints (raw hex only here): --bg-dark-ember/--bg-deep-forest/--bg-midnight, --card-graphite/--card-pine/--card-plum, --profile-quiet-grid/--profile-night-lines/--profile-calm-shapes.\n   - Non-color: --radius-sm/md/lg/xl, --space-xs/sm/md/lg/xl, --font-sans (local stack), --surface-opacity-translucent, --shadow-soft, --motion-fast/med, --safe-* (env()).\n   - ponytail: comment on legacy aliases.\n\n2. apps/mobile/app/assets/brand/ — copy 7 assets (chubzik-logo.png + 6 svg).\n\n3. shared/visual/assets.ts (~30 LOC) — export LOGO_FILE='chubzik-logo.png', MAGIC_SVG_FILES=['magic-spark',...6], BRAND_ASSET_BASE path string, FALLBACK_DECOR='soft-sparks'. Pure data, no DOM.\n\n4. shared/visual/scatter.ts (~95 LOC) — ScatterItem={x,y,rotation,scale,asset}; scatterLayout(detail): fixed LAYOUT_TABLE Record<detail,ScatterItem[]> ~6 each. Pure. Self-check via assert + `if (process.argv[1]===fileURLToPath(import.meta.url))`. Run: `npx tsx shared/visual/scatter.ts`.\n\n5. shared/visual/visual-state.ts (~120 LOC) — FALLBACK_VISUAL_STATE; ACCENT_CATALOG const (raw hex — fallback file, allowed); visualStateToCssVars(state, settings?) → Record<string,string>. Null OR disable_visual_randomness → fallback. Validate accent ∈ catalog else fallback. Returns --accent, --bg-variant, --card-variant, --profile-bg, --decor-detail, --task-button-text, --task-list-heading, --level-up-text, --empty-state-text, --reduced-motion. Self-check assert block, run `npx tsx shared/visual/visual-state.ts`.\n\n6. shared/visual/index.ts (~5) — re-export 3 modules.\n\n7. apps/mobile/visual.ts — `export * from \"../../shared/visual\"`.\n\n8. apps/mobile/app/components/Logo.vue (~70 LOC SFC) — props size/color/glow/decorative; import logoUrl from '~/assets/brand/chubzik-logo.png'; mask: url(v-bind(logoUrl)); aria-hidden when decorative; role=img+aria-label when not.\n\n9. apps/mobile/app/components/VisualBackground.vue (~90 LOC SFC) — fixed full-screen; prop decorativeDetail?: VisualState['decorative_detail'] default 'soft-sparks'; renders scatterLayout(detail) items as positioned <span> mask SVGs (import each svg url via ~/assets/brand/<name>.svg); low opacity; reads --reduced-motion CSS var via v-bind-less approach: use `@media (prefers-reduced-motion)` + check --reduced-motion var with getComputedStyle in onMounted → set local `reduced` ref. aria-hidden whole bg. color via currentColor → --brand-decoration-primary/muted tokens.\n\nWiring:\n10. main.scss — replace `:root{...}` block with `@use './tokens.scss';` (SCSS @use). Keep body/focus/.display/.text-grad/.tap/a. Remove raw hex (moved to tokens).\n11. app.vue — add <VisualBackground/> as first child inside a relative wrapper; keep NuxtLayout/NuxtPage.\n\nNOT doing: shared/api, shared/contracts, backend, admin, P10 auth pages, OD1/OD2, new VisualState fields, Math.random, Google Fonts.\n\nAcceptance: tsx self-checks pass; `cd apps/mobile && bun run typecheck` passes; rg Math.random apps shared none; rg fonts.googleapis|gstatic none; raw-hex only in tokens.scss + visual-state.ts + assets.\n\nReturn exactly one JSON object, no markdown, no prose:\n{\"ok\":bool,\"feedback\":string,\"phase\":\"plan\"}\n\nfeedback:\n- empty string if no medium/high/critical issues\n- one issue per line\n- format: [medium|high|critical]rule @loc → fix\n- drop low severity and nits\n- max 8 issues"},"timestamp":"2026-07-01T00:21:21.461Z","cwd":"/usr/projects/Диплом"}
